<hw>overutilize</hw> <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To exploit to the point of
diminishing returns; to use excessively.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> overexploit, overuse, overutilise.</syn>⟦br⟧
